Make sure that there's enough space to store decoded nibbles in when reading IMA ADPCM data.

Index: src/ima_adpcm.c
--- src/ima_adpcm.c.orig
+++ src/ima_adpcm.c
@@ -182,7 +182,12 @@ ima_reader_init (SF_PRIVATE *psf, int blockalign, int 
